.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, milk
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Beverage   | water | soy-milk | milk |

