.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | woodworking | rock-climbing |

